{
  "stem": "4187.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, again, I didn't believe him, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never believed that I could possibly die.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were taken into Theresienstadt and were taken into a particular part, which was somewhat better, in the sense that Theresienstadt, the stadt itself was-- had typhus.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And literally-- and I mean literally-- when you walked on the streets, you were walking in-- in effluence.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The stink there was something unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we were taken-- just not out-- the whole thing is that size-- but into a little compound where there was no typhus, and that point.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Neither was there any filth on the floor or on the ground or anywhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what-- we were housed in one of these barracks, and it wasn't-- certainly wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know what was going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got there on the second of May.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I can't say very much, other than I'm sure we didn't get anything to eat, because there, I do remember, by then, being awfully hungry.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we really didn't see too many Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We did see some Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we didn't see too many Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, on the 5th of May, we didn't see any Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But what we did see was Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we didn't want to believe it, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there is was-- no German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Red Cross-- in fact, we saw a Red Cross van even a day before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We saw a Red Cross van going past, which, of course, was incredibly big deal-- incredible, miracle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There's a Red Cross van.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
